   566                              <1> ; ============================================================================
   567                              <1> ; Render one frame - ultra-fast path for unchanged scenes
   568                              <1> ; Key insight: when scene is clean, we only need to update FPS text region
   569                              <1> ; (100 pixels wide x 16 pixels tall) instead of the full 3MB framebuffer
   570                              <1> ; ============================================================================
