  1199                              <1> .check_interface:
  1200                              <1>     ; Found an interface descriptor!
  1201                              <1>     ; Accept: Class=3 (HID) with ANY protocol:
  1202                              <1>     ;   Protocol=0 = Report Protocol (touchpads, composite HID)
  1203                              <1>     ;   Protocol=1 = Keyboard boot protocol  (skip)
  1204                              <1>     ;   Protocol=2 = Mouse boot protocol     (accept)
