   133                              <1> ; --- Save back buffer (RAM -> RAM) SSE2 optimized, 128 bytes/iteration ---
   134                              <1> global render_save_backbuffer
   135                              <1> render_save_backbuffer:
   136 00007526 57                  <1>     push rdi
   137 00007527 56                  <1>     push rsi
